Package com.sicomsa.dmt.svc

Class OasisSecurity

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.svc.OasisSecurity
public class OasisSecurity extends Object
Utility methods for signing envelopes according to the security requested by the WS of CFDI downloads.

    • getTimestamp

      public Instant[] getTimestamp(jakarta.xml.soap.SOAPElement parent)
      Parses the specified SOAPElement and returns an array of two instants. The first instant (0 index) will be the created instant and the second (index 1 of array) will be the expiration of the timestamp.
      Parameters:
      parent - the SOAPElement to parse
      Returns:
      an array of two instants. instant[0] = created instant; instant[1] = expires instant.
      Throws:
      SvcParseException - if there were problems while parsing
